---

Per-Client Licensing

Each end-client (legal entity) requires a separate license.
One license = one organization, unlimited SAP systems.

Examples:
- Your company, 3 SAP systems (dev/qa/prod) → 1 license
- Consultant deploys for 5 clients → 5 licenses (one per client)
- Agency manages 10 customers → 10 licenses

Sharing a single license across multiple clients is prohibited.

